# AI-Assisted Technical Book Translator

## Goal Description
Build a web application to translate highly technical computer science PDFs into Arabic Markdown files, page by page, using a local LLM via LM Studio. The app features a dual-pane UI (PDF on the left, Markdown on the right) and implements a sliding window context (N-1, N, N+1) to ensure high translation quality without breaking the context window.

